        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer139168409" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16389398075574952215">Until Forever is a powerfully written, inspiring work by a wonderful storyteller! Ms. Shortridge created realistic characters that are completely relateable to. Even if you&apos;ve never known the devastation of what addiction can do to a family, Ms. Shortridge brings it home to the reader. This is a story of love, understanding and most importantly, a faith in God and His power. <br/>A compelling story. Be ready to laugh and cry...and be moved. Highly recommended... </span>
  <span id="freeText16389398075574952215" style="display:none">Until Forever is a powerfully written, inspiring work by a wonderful storyteller! Ms. Shortridge created realistic characters that are completely relateable to. Even if you've never known the devastation of what addiction can do to a family, Ms. Shortridge brings it home to the reader. This is a story of love, understanding and most importantly, a faith in God and His power. <br />A compelling story. Be ready to laugh and cry...and be moved. Highly recommended... </span>
